summary: Good sized player home northeast of Solitude
descriptionHtml:
Goldenring Estate is a fairly large-sized player home northeast of Solitude.As of right now, the only way to get there is to swim. The house includes:

-Enchanting area with respawning cattle to constantly regenerate your soul gems
-Alchemy area with one of evey ingredient in the game, plus some potions
-Combat area with dummies
-Main hall
-Large bedroom with three pet dogs
-Blacksmith area with all blacksmithing tools

Changelog:
V1.0- initial release
